## 📌 Features

### 🎨 Welcome Page
- Bright, kid-friendly UI
- Fun, engaging visuals
- Optional real-world interaction disclaimer

### 💬 Positive Feedback System
- Encouraging responses for incorrect answers
- Positive affirmations for correct answers
- No over-rewarding (avoids unhealthy feedback loops)

### 🔥 Streak Counter
- Tracks daily progress
- Encourages consistency without pressure

### 🔔 Notifications (Planned)
- Friendly learning reminders
- Focused on motivation, not stress

